{"tid":2489084,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"超級excel 神人！！","createTime":"2021-04-14T16:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T17:27:22.000Z","uid":96796,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"31436aff96029ac383f26dfd7e1e9cc7fba01f4b","tid":2489084,"uid":96796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"因為老細依加請左3個姐姐返黎清潔，但係夜晚同早上時薪唔同，佢成日要我手計返人工，好麻煩，我想研究下可唔可以用excel整到岀黎，但發現原來我搞唔掂，所以上黎求大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姐姐人工:<br />\n中午12點至下午3點，人工$50/h<br />\n下午3點至晚上9點，人工$70/h<br />\n<br />\n有冇得係excel入，只要我入返工時間同收工時間，佢就幫我岀到果日人工幾錢<br />\n<br />\n例如: 姐姐返中午1點到晚上8點，咁人工就$450<br />\n我只要係excel入13點同20點，佢就岀到$450<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78b24caa7db91d6b73f501b6bef9148090051d4","tid":2489084,"uid":108078,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人工就你袋 嘢就我做?"},{"pid":"3bc2b1e20c7eccfd73825073a84f34a3333ee62e","tid":2489084,"uid":134087,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"揾個表列曬0000-2400每個鐘幾錢再compare 時間囉"},{"pid":"8c538cb9ab563fab65a1e678f91fb38a68cacc53","tid":2489084,"uid":2377,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"都係if 嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c56e9f5b73b9e5526c78053304f961ed9e2c73c","tid":2489084,"uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"用if 咪得囉 <br />\nif t1&lt;=15 就 (t1-13)*50<br />\nt2&gt;15 就 (t2-15)*70"},{"pid":"ba1a7bdaf4d615ccfd743429c110e96cf